::GlobalConfiguration.tooltipDismissDelay
The time (in seconds) before a <b>tooltip</b> disappears,
when no other action is taken.

::GlobalConfiguration.autodrawLatency
The time (one unit stands for 20 ms) that must pass between
a keystroke and the redrawal of a diagram.

::GlobalConfiguration.autoScroll
If checked, you will see the arrow representing the message
that you are currently typing.

::GlobalConfiguration.autostartServer
If checked, on startup the server that accepts connections
for transmitting diagram texts will be started automatically.

::GlobalConfiguration.autoUpdate
If checked, the diagram will be updated when no key has been
typed for a certain (typically small) amount of time.


